    "Title": "Locate Missing Contractors",
    "TitleKey": "Hockcrow_SearchBody_VeryHard_Title_001",
    "Description": "Hockrow Agency \nCase File #MP12854\nLead Investigator: Arken Mallor\n\nCase Summary:\nWe have been asked to track down two contractors who work for a client of ours after they lost contact with them. They were last known to be traveling together in ~mission(System). Until their exact situation can be assessed, our client is stuck in a waiting pattern. \n\nContract Investigator Actions:\nLocate <EM4>~mission(MissingPersonList)</EM4> at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and confirm their status. \n\nIf they are deceased, examine the body closely so we can verify their death via your mobiGlas.\n\nAdditional Notes:\nYou'll be heading into what is regarded as a particularly dangerous spot. Backup is highly recommended for this encounter.",
    "DescriptionKey": "Hockcrow_SearchBody_VeryHard_Description_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hockrow Agency \nCase File #MP12854\nLead Investigator: Arken Mallor\n\nCase Summary:\nWe have been asked to track down two contractors who work for a client of ours after they lost contact with them. They were last known to be traveling together in Nyx. Until their exact situation can be assessed, our client is stuck in a waiting pattern. \n\nContract Investigator Actions:\nLocate <EM4>[MissingPersonList]</EM4> at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> and confirm their status. \n\nIf they are deceased, examine the body closely so we can verify their death via your mobiGlas.\n\nAdditional Notes:\nYou'll be heading into what is regarded as a particularly dangerous spot. Backup is highly recommended for this encounter.",
